 singer 
songwriter James Blunt. Recorded in Los Angeles 
and produced
 by Tim Rothrock (Beck, Elliot Smith, Badly Drawn Boy), 
the album
 sees Blunt draw on various life experiences for inspiration,
 including hi
s spell in the army serving as
 part of a NATO peacekeeping unit in Kosovo. The single &#039;High&#039; is also included.
